description: These were the most heartstopping videos of 2025. In January, a Jacksonville, Florida, sheriff was helping to change a tire on the side of a bridge when a suspected drunk driver in a pickup truck hit his car. In February, a kayaker almost became lunch for a whale in Chile. In August, food bloggers Nina Unrated and Patrick Blackwood were eating when a car crashed through the restaurant. Inside Edition Digital's Andrea Swindall has more.
title: The Most Heartstopping Videos Of 2025
